item.description: Hi! I’m an AI enthusiast with good knowledge in the areas of machine learning and experience in building AI for the perception of self-driving cars, with a focus on deep learning, computer vision and image processing! Since I was a kid, I love cars as much as I love my family! That’s right, there’s no trade-off. After a big deal of talking with myself, motivated to develop software for Autonomous and Electric vehicles.
